OL,6,FThe framework is a core set of
OL,7,Fstandards which health and care
OL,8,Fproviders must comply with to meet the
OL,9,Fexpectations of healthcare users.
OL,11,FThe framework also aims to standardise
OL,12,Fhow providers are assessed on the
OL,13,Fisland.
OL,15,FThe Jersey Care Commission has worked
OL,16,Fwith the (CQC) to develop the
OL,17,FStandards of Jersey.
