OL,3,CJersey to consider changing how it
OL,4,Cregulates health and care providers
OL,6,FThe CQC has recently put into force a
OL,7,Fsingle assessment framework for health
OL,8,Fand social care providers across
OL,9,FEngland.
OL,11,FInspectors will follow five guiding
OL,12,Fprinciples to review a service:
OL,13,Fwhether the service is safe,
OL,14,Feffective, caring, responsive and well-
OL,15,Fled.
OL,17,FThere will be no change to how
OL,18,Fexisting providers already registered
OL,19,Fwith the Commission will be reviewed.
