OL,3,CJersey to consider changing how it
OL,4,Cregulates health and care providers
OL,6,FThe Jersey Care Commission has said:
OL,7,F"This proposed change will enable the
OL,8,FCommission to provide independent
OL,9,Fassurance, promote best practices and
OL,10,Fimprove health and social care
OL,11,Foutcomes for the people of Jersey."
OL,13,FJersey residents will have until
OL,14,FFriday 31 May to submit their thoughts.
